# Anima agent rule

Before planning or coding, read `AGENTS.md` at the repo root.

That file is the source of truth for:
- what Anima is
- current build phase / status
- what to do next
- security rules for the NanoGPT API key

When you finish meaningful work, update `AGENTS.md` (status, checkboxes, code map, next actions).

Never commit API keys or put them in source files. Use in-app Settings + `ApiKeyService`.
